      "seed": 1336872725,
      "version": 1292,
      "versionNonce": 1561042293,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "创建函数 function handleRemoteControl(\n    command: string, chatJid: string, msg: NewMessage\n) {\n    从registeredGroups中以chatJid为键查找RegisteredGroup group, 且要求为主组(.isMain);\n    从channels中查找包含chatJid的Channel channel\n    1. 如果command为\"/remote-control\"则调用startRemoteControl(msg.sender, chatJid, 当前目\n录)\n        并将返回结果通过channel.sendMessage()发送\n    2. 如果command!=\"/remote-control\"则调用stopRemoteControl()\n        并将返回结果通过channel.sendMessage()发送\n}",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "wwl_wzG0gH14XG8IyatwE",
      "originalText": "创建函数 function handleRemoteControl(\n    command: string, chatJid: string, msg: NewMessage\n) {\n    从registeredGroups中以chatJid为键查找RegisteredGroup group, 且要求为主组(.isMain);\n    从channels中查找包含chatJid的Channel channel\n    1. 如果command为\"/remote-control\"则调用startRemoteControl(msg.sender, chatJid, 当前目录)\n        并将返回结果通过channel.sendMessage()发送\n    2. 如果command!=\"/remote-control\"则调用stopRemoteControl()\n        并将返回结果通过channel.sendMessage()发送\n}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
