      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 如果state.pendingTasks列表非空，则只取队首元素task，调用runTask(groupJid, task)\n2. 如果state.pendingMessages=true，则调用runForGroup(groupJid, \"drain\")\n3. 如果以上两者都不满足，则说明当前队列已空闲，直接调用drainWaiting()",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "-5K2Z6R-XliIixnnR4vtO",
      "originalText": "1. 如果state.pendingTasks列表非空，则只取队首元素task，调用runTask(groupJid, task)\n2. 如果state.pendingMessages=true，则调用runForGroup(groupJid, \"drain\")\n3. 如果以上两者都不满足，则说明当前队列已空闲，直接调用drainWaiting()",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
