      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 从waitingGroups中取出一个GroupJid nextJid\n2. 如果其state.pendingTasks列表非空，调用\nrunTask(groupJid, task)\n3. 如果其state.pendingMessages=true，则调用\nrunForGroup(groupJid, \"drain\")\n4. 如果以上两者都不满足，则说明所有队列均空闲，直接\nreturn即可",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "H9m2HZRr-ZH7y1sH0Lppf",
      "originalText": "1. 从waitingGroups中取出一个GroupJid nextJid\n2. 如果其state.pendingTasks列表非空，调用runTask(groupJid, task)\n3. 如果其state.pendingMessages=true，则调用runForGroup(groupJid, \"drain\")\n4. 如果以上两者都不满足，则说明所有队列均空闲，直接return即可",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
