    {
      "id": "SQErKuG5uQYppikgVqVyF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -924.7881648280209,
      "y": 5417.198376568915,
      "width": 525.6000366210938,
      "height": 400,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "5EsdGFu49fNB7C3bWOGvA",
      "index": "bDF",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1502913211,
      "version": 1709,
      "versionNonce": 672006715,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 根据chatJid，从全局变量Record<string, RegisteredGroup>\nregisteredGroups中获取RegisteredGroup实例group。\n2. 根据chatJid，从全局变量Channel[] channels查找包含\nchatJid的Channel实例channel。\n3. 根据GroupJid作为chat_jid，先通过Record<String, String>\n得到时间戳，再调用getMessagesSince()查询messages表，得到\n历史NewMessage[] messages。\n4. 调用router.ts的formatMessages()，格式化messages为字符\n串<context timezone=\"...\"/><messages><message sender=\"...\"\ntime=\"...\">{content}</message></messages>\n5. 调用channel.setTyping(chatJid, true)表示Agent正在回复\n6. 调用主函数提供的runAgent(group, prompt, chatJid,\ncallback)用于获取大模型回复，去除<internal>思考内容后调\n用channel.sendMessage(chatJid, text)\n7. 在IDLE_TIMEOUT时间后调用closeStdin(groupJid)，让容器执\n行下一个任务；或者如果大模型回复成功，则调用\nqueue.notifyIdle()，在state.pendingTasks非空时立即调用\ncloseStdin(groupJid)。\n8. 如果大模型回复失败，则回滚时间戳这一游标，用于后续重\n新消费Message。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "Opw19v1d8G6GtNmyP9BlL",
      "originalText": "1. 根据chatJid，从全局变量Record<string, RegisteredGroup> registeredGroups中获取RegisteredGroup实例group。\n2. 根据chatJid，从全局变量Channel[] channels查找包含chatJid的Channel实例channel。\n3. 根据GroupJid作为chat_jid，先通过Record<String, String>得到时间戳，再调用getMessagesSince()查询messages表，得到历史NewMessage[] messages。\n4. 调用router.ts的formatMessages()，格式化messages为字符串<context timezone=\"...\"/><messages><message sender=\"...\" time=\"...\">{content}</message></messages>\n5. 调用channel.setTyping(chatJid, true)表示Agent正在回复\n6. 调用主函数提供的runAgent(group, prompt, chatJid, callback)用于获取大模型回复，去除<internal>思考内容后调用channel.sendMessage(chatJid, text)\n7. 在IDLE_TIMEOUT时间后调用closeStdin(groupJid)，让容器执行下一个任务；或者如果大模型回复成功，则调用queue.notifyIdle()，在state.pendingTasks非空时立即调用closeStdin(groupJid)。\n8. 如果大模型回复失败，则回滚时间戳这一游标，用于后续重新消费Message。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
