      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "创建函数 function loadState() {\n    读取数据库的router_state表，加载lastTimestamp字段\n    读取数据库的router_state表，加载lastAgentTimeStamp字段\n    读取数据库的sessions表的所有Session，整理成Record<group_folder, session_id>保存到session字段\n    读取数据库的registered_groups表，整理成Record<jid, RegisteredGroup>保存到registeredGroups\n}",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "3cSmsLZv9tgoP4SlZf348",
      "originalText": "创建函数 function loadState() {\n    读取数据库的router_state表，加载lastTimestamp字段\n    读取数据库的router_state表，加载lastAgentTimeStamp字段\n    读取数据库的sessions表的所有Session，整理成Record<group_folder, session_id>保存到session字段\n    读取数据库的registered_groups表，整理成Record<jid, RegisteredGroup>保存到registeredGroups\n}",
