    },
    {
      "id": "QJORgUGdnyVWQ4sU1K55x",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -975.1171188769626,
      "y": 5116.210882796102,
      "width": 423.19989013671875,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "5EsdGFu49fNB7C3bWOGvA",
      "index": "bDW",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 239724027,
      "version": 1430,
      "versionNonce": 1080285691,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "更新状态机，同时向GroupQueue提交申请资源的请\n求\n1. 将taskId写入pendingTasks队尾\n2. 如果容器在休眠，则调用closeStdin()\n3. 如果队列资源已耗尽，则则需要将groupJid提交\n到全局的waitingGroups",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "E-UrixCFx08qXabZZs4A4",
      "originalText": "更新状态机，同时向GroupQueue提交申请资源的请求\n1. 将taskId写入pendingTasks队尾\n2. 如果容器在休眠，则调用closeStdin()\n3. 如果队列资源已耗尽，则则需要将groupJid提交到全局的waitingGroups",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "Oey9FgrQ7XIxeuqolcpZN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -981.9673952089092,
      "y": 5024.712044596146,
      "width": 446.5640778141844,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "5EsdGFu49fNB7C3bWOGvA",
      "index": "bDX",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 28405403,
      "version": 1486,
      "versionNonce": 1272649525,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "任务入队前发送资源请求✅\n    - void enqueueTask(groupJid, taskId)",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "任务入队前发送资源请求✅\n    - void enqueueTask(groupJid, taskId)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "QvuVZvbrMM5H57KQBmdC0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -308.24487819163505,
      "y": 5899.555306216087,
      "width": 911,
      "height": 300,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#f08c00",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "5EsdGFu49fNB7C3bWOGvA",
      "index": "bDY",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1620757179,
      "version": 1629,
      "versionNonce": 1147986587,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "GroupQueue为每个Jid维护一个队列。\n每个队列优先处理自己维护的Task列表，调用Task自带的处理函数；\n然后处理数据库维护的Message列表，统一拼接成一条消息，调用main()提供的处理函数\n当某个队列处理完Task和Message后，会去处理别的队列，直到全部处理完毕为止。\n\nTask是Agent自己设定的定时任务，是一次性的操作，即使失败了也会马上丢弃\nMessage是用户发来的消息，是一个长期的回合，必须保证数据的持久化\n两者共用一个容器池\n\nNanoClaw在队列消费时使用了大量的嵌套，为了避免DFS爆栈，NodeJS的解决方案是：\n调用嵌套方法时使用await，因此每次可以立即返回Promise，而非层层嵌套\n创建的异步任务会交给主线程到微任务队列中消费。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "GroupQueue为每个Jid维护一个队列。\n每个队列优先处理自己维护的Task列表，调用Task自带的处理函数；\n然后处理数据库维护的Message列表，统一拼接成一条消息，调用main()提供的处理函数\n当某个队列处理完Task和Message后，会去处理别的队列，直到全部处理完毕为止。\n\nTask是Agent自己设定的定时任务，是一次性的操作，即使失败了也会马上丢弃\nMessage是用户发来的消息，是一个长期的回合，必须保证数据的持久化\n两者共用一个容器池\n\nNanoClaw在队列消费时使用了大量的嵌套，为了避免DFS爆栈，NodeJS的解决方案是：\n调用嵌套方法时使用await，因此每次可以立即返回Promise，而非层层嵌套\n创建的异步任务会交给主线程到微任务队列中消费。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
