      "text": "1. 提供Map<String(name), ChannelFactory> registry及其CRUD方法\n\n2. 定义interface ChannelOpts = {OnInBoundMessge, OnChatMetadata,\nRecord<String, RegisteredGroup>}，用于作为Channel的工厂方法\nstd::function<Channel(ChannelOpts)> ChannelFactory的实参",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
