      "versionNonce": 1346795925,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1. 设置全局变量schedulerRunning = true;\n2. 每隔SCHEDULER_POLL_INTERVAL就执行一次loop()，loop()从数据库表scheduled_tasks获\n取现在需要执行的任务，遍历调用deps.queue.enqueueTask(task.chatJid, task.id, ()=>\n{runTask(task, deps)})。",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "ZbOnPHeJpcIcD8jpzmPlq",
      "originalText": "1. 设置全局变量schedulerRunning = true;\n2. 每隔SCHEDULER_POLL_INTERVAL就执行一次loop()，loop()从数据库表scheduled_tasks获取现在需要执行的任务，遍历调用deps.queue.enqueueTask(task.chatJid, task.id, ()=>{runTask(task, deps)})。",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
