      "seed": 560510709,
      "version": 5196,
      "versionNonce": 1470146837,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774241841007,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "如果是主群组，则挂载 `cwd` -> /workspace/project, 只读\n如果是主群组，且存在`cwd`/.env，则挂载 /dev/null -> .env，只读\n\n如果是非主群组，则挂载 `cwd`/groups/global -> /workspace/global，只读\n\n挂载 {DATA_DIR}/ipc/{group_folder}/ -> /workspace/group，可读写\n创建 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/.claude/settings.json，写入CLAUDE_CODE配置\n复制 `cwd`/container/skills -> `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/.claude/skills\n挂载 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/.claude/ -> /home/node/.claude，可读写\n创建 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/messages或tasks或input\n挂载 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder} -> /workspace/ipc，可读写\n复制 `cwd`/container/agent-runner/src -> {DATA_DIR}/sessions/{group_folder}/agent-runner-src\n挂载 {DATA_DIR}/sessions/{group_folder}/agent-runner-src -> /app/src，可读写\n挂载 validateAdditionalMounts给定的若干白名单挂载点",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "3FtQEQiEW5RqshCgaET_h",
      "originalText": "如果是主群组，则挂载 `cwd` -> /workspace/project, 只读\n如果是主群组，且存在`cwd`/.env，则挂载 /dev/null -> .env，只读\n\n如果是非主群组，则挂载 `cwd`/groups/global -> /workspace/global，只读\n\n挂载 {DATA_DIR}/ipc/{group_folder}/ -> /workspace/group，可读写\n创建 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/.claude/settings.json，写入CLAUDE_CODE配置\n复制 `cwd`/container/skills -> `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/.claude/skills\n挂载 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/.claude/ -> /home/node/.claude，可读写\n创建 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder}/messages或tasks或input\n挂载 `cwd`/data/sessions/{group_folder} -> /workspace/ipc，可读写\n复制 `cwd`/container/agent-runner/src -> {DATA_DIR}/sessions/{group_folder}/agent-runner-src\n挂载 {DATA_DIR}/sessions/{group_folder}/agent-runner-src -> /app/src，可读写\n挂载 validateAdditionalMounts给定的若干白名单挂载点",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
