    {
      "id": "1rv2cihx-dRkdfGaX7Z_F",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3249.1438666112676,
      "y": 1284.1987323532057,
      "width": 588.799560546875,
      "height": 280,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "4_6_Cam0XscSgoROWcWKn",
      "index": "bH7zzz",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1502525595,
      "version": 930,
      "versionNonce": 1224286293,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774240991706,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "形参说明：\n- prompt: 初始Prompt\n- sessionId: (containerInput或runQuery()).sessionId\n- mcpServerPath: \"./ipc-mcp-stdio.js\"\n- sdkEnv: 进程的环境变量\n- resumeAt: runQuery().lastAssistantUuid\n\n1. 设置循环任务: 如果存在/workspace/ipc/input/_close则退出，否则\n把drainIpcOutput()的值扔到stream.push()。\n2. 加载/workspace/global/CLAUDE.md和/workspace/extra/{文件夹}\n3. 调用Anthropic SDK的query()，得到API的JSON响应message。\nmessage.type字段可能有\"assistant\"/\"uuid\"/\"system\"/\"init\"/reulst\n等类型，一律输出到STDOUT\n4. 返回API返回的{sessionId, lastAssistantUuid, closedDuringQuery}",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "K3L7CInf7g1ZVRdahs08e",
      "originalText": "形参说明：\n- prompt: 初始Prompt\n- sessionId: (containerInput或runQuery()).sessionId\n- mcpServerPath: \"./ipc-mcp-stdio.js\"\n- sdkEnv: 进程的环境变量\n- resumeAt: runQuery().lastAssistantUuid\n\n1. 设置循环任务: 如果存在/workspace/ipc/input/_close则退出，否则把drainIpcOutput()的值扔到stream.push()。\n2. 加载/workspace/global/CLAUDE.md和/workspace/extra/{文件夹}\n3. 调用Anthropic SDK的query()，得到API的JSON响应message。message.type字段可能有\"assistant\"/\"uuid\"/\"system\"/\"init\"/reulst\n等类型，一律输出到STDOUT\n4. 返回API返回的{sessionId, lastAssistantUuid, closedDuringQuery}",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
