      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "工具列表: 'Bash', 'Read', 'Write', 'Edit', 'Glob', 'Grep', 'WebSearch',\n'WebFetch', 'Task', 'TaskOutput', 'TaskStop', 'TeamCreate', 'TeamDelete',\n'SendMessage', 'TodoWrite', 'ToolSearch', 'Skill', 'NotebookEdit',\n'mcp__nanoclaw__*'\n\nMCP服务器: \"node ./ipc-mcp-stdio.js\"，配置环境变量CHAT_JID、GROUP_FOLDER、\nIS_MAIN\n\n钩子：createPreCompactHook(containerInput.assistName)",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
